  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      We will examine how stimulation of specific brain areas with transcranial magnetic&#xD;
      stimulation (TMS) or transcranial electric stimulation (tES) changes specific aspects of&#xD;
      behavior and brain activity, in order to test hypotheses about brain behavior relationships&#xD;
      (basic research).&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
